Interface VideojsPlayer.VideojsListener

  • All Superinterfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    VideojsPlayer

    public static interface VideojsPlayer.VideojsListener
extends Serializable
    VideojsListener interface for listening for Video.js Events fired by a VideojsPlayer

    v0.1
